node.title: Multiple people injured at house during 'serious incident' in Auckland
node.description: Police are attending the scene of what they describe as a 'serious incident' in Auckland involving injuries to multiple people.
node.content:
["Police are attending the scene of what they describe as a 'serious incident' in Auckland involving injuries to multiple people.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Police received a report of an incident at an address on Glass Rd in the suburb of Mount Roskill about 9.30pm this evening.", "It is understood three people have been injured at the address.", "\"There will be a heavy Police presence in the area while enquiries are made,\" a police statement this evening said.", "No arrests have been made. Police have not confirmed whether the incident was a shooting."]
